snippet.title: Conception - Hold On (Cover by SIEG ft. Byulhae)
snippet.description:
Siegfried Song Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial
Byulhae YouTube : https://www.youtube.com/c/Byulhaeofficial

I wished I could take the heart of someone that I shouldn't be with and I thought it would be delivered through my voice if I truly believed. Once it was with me and made my years, but the moment was so brief and my world fell apart again. Nothing could remedy and I feel like I lost my passion forever.

아름다운 연주가 맘에 드셨다면 별해 님의 유튜브 꼭 방문해주세요! ;)
